<div class="app-card-container">
  
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    
    

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "profile2.jpg", width:200, height: 200, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          <div class="skill">
            <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div 
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>Throughout my 19 years of experience as a Technical Recruiter, Recruiting Manager and Managing Director, I have realized my passion for technology, and have embarked on a new path as a full stack developer.</p>

        <p>It is my mission to use my past experience working with and managing dynamic teams to be a better developer. I am driven to produce high quality websites, applications and software that people love to use.</p>

        <p>
          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#jobHistory"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="jobHistory"
        >

            Job History
          </button>

          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#education"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="education"
        >
            Education
          </button>

          <button
          class="btn btn-primary"
          type="button"
          data-toggle="collapse"
          data-target="#training"
          aria-expanded="false"
          aria-controler="training"
        >

            Training
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Enrollmentment Specialist & Student; Bottega, Leni, UT
              <br>
              May 2017 - Current
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Manager of Recruitment; Southcentral Foundation, Anchorage, AK
              <br>
              June 2015 – September 2016
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              General Manager; Alaska Executive Search, Inc., Anchorage, AK
              <br>
              July 2013 – January 2015 
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Senior Recruiter; JLG Industries, Hagerstown, MD
              <br>
              October 2011 – July 2013  
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Senior Recruiter; Manpower (contract JLG), Hagerstown, MD
              <br>
              February 2011 – September 2011  
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Managing Director; Information Technology Growth Solutions, LLC, Roanoke, VA
              <br>
              January 2007 – February 2011  
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              University of Phoenix - 2016
              <br>
              Phoenix, AZ
              <br>                 
              AA - Information Technology   
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Montgomery College - 1993-1994
              <br>
              Rockville, MD
              <br>
              Business Administration 
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              JLG - PMP Foundations
              <br>
              JLG - Six Sigma  
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="training">
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              Bottega - 2016
              <br>
              Full Stack Development (Ruby on Rails)
              <br>
              Certified Full Stack Web Developer
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              One Month Rails - 2015
              <br>
              Certificate of Completion
              <br> 
              One month interactive course on Ruby on Rails
            </div>
            <div class="about-btn-container">
              JLG - PMP Foundations
              <br>
              JLG - Six Sigma  
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

